Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.10,0:23:42.48,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}這些暫時的感傷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.69,0:23:44.94,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}只要認可就好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.15,0:23:47.99,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}因此請讓我對你說
